5
00:00:51,573 --> 00:00:59,675
who will be speaking on things you really need to know about issues currently affecting Method.

6
00:01:01,295 --> 00:01:16,058
So we're gonna get right into the questions, and Trish, the first question is, tell us, what were the reasons you became involved with all the issues facing the city of Method?

7
00:01:17,710 --> 00:01:19,290
Well, thank you for having me, John.

8
00:01:19,871 --> 00:01:20,811
It's a pleasure to be here.

9
00:01:20,831 --> 00:01:33,034
I think in May of 2024, I found some information from some neighbors that there was a methadone dispensary that was going to be going in on Salem Street.

10
00:01:33,714 --> 00:01:36,034
As an abutter, I had never been notified.

11
00:01:36,514 --> 00:01:43,336
And when I started talking to many of my neighbors and people in the neighborhood, they had not been notified either that

12
00:01:43,756 --> 00:01:45,877
this methadone dispensary was coming in.

13
00:01:46,537 --> 00:01:53,220
And so through looking at where they were going to place the methadone dispensary, it was .2 miles from an elementary school.

14
00:01:53,800 --> 00:01:57,742
So I contacted the Attorney General's office and said, this is crazy.

15
00:01:58,122 --> 00:02:04,225
How can you let a methadone dispensary be .2 miles from an elementary school?

16
00:02:04,565 --> 00:02:10,628
